name: Todd Dulaney
description: '''Todd Anthony Dulaney''' (born December 20, 1983) is an American [[gospel music]]ian, and former [[baseball|baseball player]]. His music career started in 2011, with the release of the CD version, ''Pulling Me Through''. This would be his breakthrough released upon the [[Billboard (magazine)|''Billboard'']] [[Top Gospel Albums|Gospel Albums]] chart. He would release another album, ''A Worshipper's Heart'', in 2016 with EntertainmentOne Nashville, and this would place even higher on the Gospel Albums chart.
